":766702,"uid":49274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"各位有無用過bio essence去角質隻野，要嚟洗鼻好唔好?<br />\n<br />\n我google過偏方，用海鹽搽鼻，用保鮮紙蓋住，再搭多條熱毛巾"},{"pid":"ce2114b5074f28620b75911f09f652e8385cc9e2","tid":766702,"uid":145311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"除左個鼻, 我額頭同鼻兩旁臉額啲毛孔都粗大<br />\n已經好勤力做保濕<br />\n每次敷完mask啲毛孔都縮細左好多<br />\n但瞓醒出番油又打回原形<br />\n美容師懷疑過我塊臉有蟎蟲<br />\n真心有冇皮膚科醫生推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c568687843a7ca417de3018ed73569ed1284b22c","tid":766702,"uid":52539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:16:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2u1TwGWbXvU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2u1TwGWbXvU&d=cuRonXnQ5zwfj9F74ebQ10bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c75c44fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2u1TwGWbXvU</a><br />\n<br />\n1.保濕&amp;皮脂線出油唔關係 自己GOOGLE<br />\n2.水楊酸/杏仁酸 用低%慢慢 最少半年時間<br />\n3.針清/鼻貼之後收毛孔都係冇用 如果整傷左就係整傷左<br />\n4.物理性磨沙果D好易出事 過眼雲煙<br />\n<br />\n自己研究下啦 其實上黎問都係多餘 9成都係跟班YOUTUBE真心推介自圓其說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n輕鬆美膚<br />\nMedPartner"},{"pid":"69c332bf170f095e277e4c0bb7dc563aa655d678","tid":766702,"uid":52539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://6897.cyberbiz.tw/s/files/6897/ckeditor/pictures/content_3d47d8d8-9c60-45ee-93f1-2e260b0c27cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F6897.cyberbiz.tw%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F6897%2Fckeditor%2Fpictures%2Fcontent_3d47d8d8-9c60-45ee-93f1-2e260b0c27cc.jpg&h=a7da816f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢D先係粉刺 比你地想像大粒好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鼻貼果D係痴住毛普通皮脂黎 仲會整傷D皮膚搞到毛孔粗大 愈大就愈多野痴出黎 惡性LOOP 諗起都爽YY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n