8ac56\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.ezskin.com.tw/blogs/%E9%99%B3%E7%9A%AE%E9%9D%A0%E8%85%B021-30%E9%9B%86/15214</a><br />\n<br />\n不過毛孔大小係天生 冇得強求 <br />\n冇哂粉刺都只係將你原本既毛孔推到最細<br />\n不過係你都要強求既話就要打激光 打腫D細胞 好似你保濕咁 變哂肥仔間接整細毛孔"},{"pid":"fd9a20a75389730828382bc0e60d15c662337323","tid":766702,"uid":52539,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"其實我都已經好少出聲 唔係幾想再講 根本月經 <br />\n<br />\n根本好多人係想買野 唔係想整好塊面 叫你地認認真真研究下做下功課就當廢UP<br />\n<br />\n最好就話比佢地聽 樓下萬寧有得買 邊隻牌子 用完咩事都冇哂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc94a1a9f2202f89cd16fb4bee535d7c82fb48fc","tid":766702,"uid":35863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"泥mask"},{"pid":"82d47dc9cd0ced452a2a8d3b7fc073d5e89df614","tid":766702,"uid":145311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f8b919928e6924bcb905bd72efcf56571bc6e613","tid":766702,"uid":52539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce2114b5074f28620b75911f09f652e8385cc9e2","tid":766702,"uid":145311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"除左個鼻, 我額頭同鼻兩旁臉額啲毛孔都粗大<br />\n已經好勤力做保濕<br />\n每次敷完mask啲毛孔都縮細左好多<br />\n但瞓醒出番油又打回原形<br />\n美容師懷疑過我塊臉有蟎蟲<br />\n真心有冇皮膚科醫生推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:33:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://shop.ezskin.com.tw/blogs/%E9%99%B3%E7%9A%AE%E9%9D%A0%E8%85%B031-40%E9%9B%86/16598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.ezskin.com.tw%2Fblogs%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E7%259A%25AE%25E9%259D%25A0%25E8%2585%25B031-40%25E9%259B%2586%2F16598&d=cuRonXnQ5zwfj9F74ebQ10bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=454451f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.ezskin.com.tw/blogs/%E9%99%B3%E7%9A%AE%E9%9D%A0%E8%85%B031-40%E9%9B%86/16598</a><br />\n<br />\n蟎蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你就係太勤力敷mask 姐係好似你沖完涼出黎 毛孔好似好細咁 過一陣又打回原形<br />\n飲飽水咪粒粒細胞都肥仔咁間接整